sourcesContent: import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; @Component({ selector: 'app-dashboard', templateUrl: './dashboard.component.html', styleUrls: ['./dashboard.component.scss'] }) export class DashboardComponent { menuItems = [ { title: 'Post', link: '/post' }, { title: 'Profile', link: '/profile' }, { title: 'Setting', link: '/setting' } ]; }
